content:
@Kk81, thank you for updating the statement.

@User123, what do you think of the updated statement, and our responses to your suggestion of including the "fewest summit" rule?

Also, I'd like to assess whether the puzzle should be kept open for approval. I'd prefer not to have it approved while significant changes may still be made (it's already been approved by one reviewer…). How's your review coming along, and do you have an estimate of when you might finish? Do the outstanding items feel substantial, or more on the minor side?

There's absolutely no rush at all; I just want to get a sense of timing. If it'd be helpful, I can suggest that the author switch back to WIP to allow for more review time.

Many thanks.
